// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0604 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 7aa64339-5921-5c29-9340-79df65189f6b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:22.04*")
